      "\n",
      "--- Outlier report (IQR method) ---\n",
      "                         lower_bound  upper_bound  n_outliers  pct_outliers\n",
      "order_value_eur               -47.38       149.95       742.0          6.18\n",
      "shipping_distance_km         -377.59      1258.91       358.0          2.98\n",
